WEBVTT

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:59.270
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:01.590
for joining us again today. We're

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:03.190
excited to be here. We have a lot to

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:05.670
talk about and pray about tonight.

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:08.469
First off, I want to tell you a cool

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:11.589
testimony. This testimony was a shock

00:02:11.599 --> 00:02:13.589
and awe to me, but of course we all

00:02:13.599 --> 00:02:17.670
know that Jesus is wonderful.

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:20.309
Several weeks ago, the Lord instructed

00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:23.190
me to go over to this gentleman's house,

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:24.949
and He said, "I want you to go over and

00:02:24.959 --> 00:02:27.830
I want you to pray for him because

00:02:27.830 --> 00:02:27.840
the

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:30.309
arteries of his heart are clogged and he

00:02:30.319 --> 00:02:32.229
doesn't know it. There's a

00:02:32.229 --> 00:02:32.239
blockage."And

00:02:32.239 --> 00:02:34.470
He said, "I

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:36.150
want you to go over and lay hands on

00:02:36.160 --> 00:02:38.790
him because in the

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.670
natural, his heart is about ready to

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:43.430
have a heart

00:02:43.430 --> 00:02:43.440
attack."I

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:45.350
had a vision where the Lord

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:47.670
showed me his wife was a widow. She was

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:49.990
alone and they're not

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.750
that old. I mean, they're not elder

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:55.270
elders, but they're not

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:56.309
old. I don't even think they're old

00:02:56.319 --> 00:02:59.190
enough to be my mom and my dad, do you?

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.509
No. So, the Lord warned me about

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:04.149
this man and He said, "I want you to

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:06.710
go over there and pray for

00:03:06.710 --> 00:03:06.720
him."Well,

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:09.030
when I was there, I said, "I'm not

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:10.390
trying to scare you, but this is what

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:13.270
the Lord is telling me. So, I want

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:14.710
to pray for you. Is it okay if I pray

00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:16.070
for you?"Because I'm not just going to

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:18.149
lay hands on anyone who doesn't want

00:03:18.149 --> 00:03:18.159
me

00:03:18.159 --> 00:03:20.790
to pray for them. But he asked me

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:22.630
when I walked in. He said,

00:03:22.630 --> 00:03:22.640
"Brandon,

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:25.910
I felt inside

00:03:25.920 --> 00:03:28.550
that maybe you could pray for

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:30.869
something that I'm having a need

00:03:30.869 --> 00:03:30.879
of."And

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:32.630
I said, "Well,

00:03:32.630 --> 00:03:32.640
okay."He

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:35.750
said, "I have two

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:37.350
hernias

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:39.589
in my body that are pretty severe, and

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:42.390
I'm scheduled to have

00:03:42.390 --> 00:03:42.400
surgery."I

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.229
believe it was a couple of weeks out.

00:03:44.239 --> 00:03:46.229
And

00:03:46.239 --> 00:03:50.149
he said, "But I'm believing

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:52.550
that if you pray for me and we

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:54.710
agree together, that I'll

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:57.670
be

00:03:57.670 --> 00:03:57.680
healed."Because

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:59.190
certain people know

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:00.869
that the Lord has put healing in my

00:04:00.879 --> 00:04:03.030
hands. I don't make it a widely known

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:07.509
thing. I know the Lord told me

00:04:07.519 --> 00:04:09.990
when Ralph Wilkerson touched my hands

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.070
and he said, "These hands are

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:13.589
going to have fire in them."He touched

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:14.869
my hands, he touched the palm of each

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:16.310
one of my hands, and he said, "I'm

00:04:16.320 --> 00:04:17.349
putting a double portion of the

00:04:17.359 --> 00:04:19.670
anointing on my life on you."This is

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:21.270
Ralph Wilkerson at Melodyland Christian

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:25.510
Center. Back in 2001 he did this.

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:34.390
Ever since then, my hands

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:36.550
get hot with fire, but I never know

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:37.270
when it's going to happen when I'm

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:38.870
praying for somebody. Sometimes

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:41.510
it's like touching a cold stove.

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:44.629
In this situation, he said, "Will you

00:04:44.639 --> 00:04:47.990
please pray for me for these

00:04:47.990 --> 00:04:48.000
hernias?"And

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:50.629
I was like, "Okay, well, I came here

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:53.110
to pray for your heart.

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:55.110
The Lord told me about your

00:04:55.110 --> 00:04:55.120
heart."And

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:56.710
he goes, "Wow."I could see he

00:04:56.710 --> 00:04:56.720
was

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:58.150
kind of concerned about it on his face,

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.350
but I didn't want to make a big deal out

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:00.790
of it or let him know what I

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:03.030
saw in the spirit, which was that this man was about

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:04.710
to die.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:08.950
And so I prayed for him.

00:05:08.960 --> 00:05:11.749
I put his hand on his groin

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:13.350
area and I put my hand on top because

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:14.790
it's awkward—I'm not going to touch a

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:16.230
man like that.

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:18.790
I prayed

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:21.110
for him a prayer of faith and I laid

00:05:21.120 --> 00:05:24.150
hands on him. I didn't hear anything, just

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:25.749
like it was with the man

00:05:25.759 --> 00:05:29.430
with the lungs

00:05:29.430 --> 00:05:29.440
who

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:31.189
got healed and got two

00:05:31.189 --> 00:05:31.199
brand-new

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:33.670
lungs. The doctor told him he was going

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:36.469
to die and he needed a lung transplant.

00:05:36.479 --> 00:05:37.909
Anybody knows that story? I've told it

00:05:37.919 --> 00:05:41.670
before. Well, a couple of weeks

00:05:41.670 --> 00:05:41.680
go

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:46.310
by and my wife got a text from his wife.

00:05:49.919 --> 00:05:54.629
She said, "Good morning. I

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:57.270
have to share a prayer report with

00:05:57.280 --> 00:06:00.790
you. My husband has been going to

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:04.070
doctors for over two years.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:07.590
He was diagnosed with double hernias and

00:06:07.600 --> 00:06:10.230
they have been waiting on him to have

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:14.390
surgery. He's been putting it off

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:17.670
and had so much stress about having

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:20.950
surgery for quite some time. He went

00:06:20.960 --> 00:06:24.790
again to a new doctor last month,

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:27.590
right after he asked Brandon to

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:31.990
pray for him. He had several tests and

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:35.990
ultrasounds again. The results came back

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:39.110
yesterday. It's a total answer to

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:41.430
prayer.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:45.270
I had to share below a picture of the

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:48.070
report

00:06:48.070 --> 00:06:48.080
findings."The

00:06:48.080 --> 00:06:51.029
power of God touched him; the

00:06:51.029 --> 00:06:51.039
hernias

00:06:51.039 --> 00:06:53.909
are completely gone,

00:06:53.919 --> 00:06:57.830
both of them. And the doctor said,

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:02.710
"You don't have to have surgery.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:05.430
All the hernia and all the evidence of

00:07:05.440 --> 00:07:07.990
the hernia, even through the ultrasound,

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.710
is completely gone."And he had had this

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:12.070
and he was suffering. It hurt; he said

00:07:12.080 --> 00:07:14.469
it was very uncomfortable. Of course, he

00:07:14.479 --> 00:07:17.270
had two major hernias and they had

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:20.150
scheduled him six

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:22.469
weeks out from having the surgery

00:07:22.479 --> 00:07:23.510
because he was like, "I'm just going to

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:25.830
go ahead and do it."So the power of God

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:28.070
touched him and I was just giving all

00:07:28.080 --> 00:07:30.469
the glory to the Lord for it.

00:07:30.479 --> 00:07:33.670
Isn't Jesus

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:36.469
wonderful? I went over there to give him

00:07:36.479 --> 00:07:39.189
the word about the heart and Jesus

00:07:39.199 --> 00:07:42.070
touches the hernias

00:07:42.070 --> 00:07:42.080
that were

00:07:42.080 --> 00:07:44.870
bothering him.

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:46.790
I thought, we are in the last

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:49.110
days. I talked to my

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:51.189
friend Billy Burke today.

00:07:51.199 --> 00:07:55.670
I love that man.

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:57.270
I know for a fact what the Lord has

00:07:57.280 --> 00:07:58.869
shown me about his ministry and what's

00:07:58.879 --> 00:08:00.309
going to happen in the days ahead with

00:08:00.319 --> 00:08:01.830
great signs and wonders, even more than

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:04.390
what he already walks in. But I know

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:07.110
whenever

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:09.589
the Lord told me

00:08:09.589 --> 00:08:09.599
"cross-pollination,"when

00:08:09.599 --> 00:08:11.749
you start talking to people that

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:14.230
walk underneath an anointing and you

00:08:14.230 --> 00:08:14.240
sow

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:16.710
into their ministry and you believe by

00:08:16.720 --> 00:08:20.869
faith, it's a covenant. You

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:23.110
start giving and you start believing.

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:24.550
I already know what the Lord has

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:27.029
told me, that I'll walk in healings,

00:08:27.039 --> 00:08:28.550
but I don't know when it's going to come

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:31.430
on like that full-time. All I know is

00:08:31.440 --> 00:08:33.350
the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm going to

00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:35.509
use you one day with this and I'll use

00:08:35.519 --> 00:08:37.430
Diana with you."And even Billy has

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:39.909
given Diana words about how she'll pray

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:42.709
for babies that are dead in

00:08:42.719 --> 00:08:44.870
the womb—where the mother has gotten a

00:08:44.880 --> 00:08:47.670
bad report of a baby that has been

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:49.430
diagnosed as not alive

00:08:49.430 --> 00:08:49.440
anymore—and

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.190
the power of God, by laying hands

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.630
on the mother, is going

00:08:52.640 --> 00:08:54.790
to raise that baby from the dead. I

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:57.509
truly believe that in the resurrection

00:08:57.519 --> 00:09:00.070
power of the Lord Jesus. I was so

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:02.949
excited for him that

00:09:02.949 --> 00:09:02.959
he doesn't

00:09:02.959 --> 00:09:06.070
have to have surgery now and that he

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:08.550
got such a great report.

00:09:08.560 --> 00:09:11.190
I don't

00:09:11.190 --> 00:09:11.200
want

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.470
things like that to ever

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:14.310
just bypass you; I want to always stay

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:16.470
in awe of Jesus for what He's done in

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:20.470
these last days. Oh, Father, thank you.

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:22.710
And like He said, "Brandon, never

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:26.230
take a miracle for granted. Never

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:29.430
look at it as insignificant

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:32.070
when I touch somebody. For when there

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:33.990
are so many miracles that are about to

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:36.470
take place, don't become familiar with

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.949
my glory. Don't become familiar with

00:09:38.959 --> 00:09:41.430
what I'm doing in ministry."I know

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.990
beyond a shadow of a doubt. I've seen dogs

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:47.670
raised from the dead. I've seen

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:49.990
people carrying an

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:52.870
oxygen tank behind them, completely

00:09:52.870 --> 00:09:52.880
grayed

00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:55.110
out on the verge of death. I've laid hands on

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.110
them and God gave them two

00:09:57.110 --> 00:09:57.120
brand-new

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:58.710
lungs. They came back. The doctor said,

00:09:58.710 --> 00:09:58.720
"We're

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:00.550
taking you off the donor's

00:10:00.550 --> 00:10:00.560
list,"completely

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:02.389
healed by the power of God. They

00:10:02.389 --> 00:10:02.399
were

00:10:02.399 --> 00:10:04.790
delivered after they

00:10:04.800 --> 00:10:08.150
sprayed Roundup on the ground for

00:10:08.150 --> 00:10:08.160
40-some

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:10.389
years for the city and breathing in all

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:12.070
those chemicals every single day

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:14.389
destroyed their lungs. He had

00:10:14.389 --> 00:10:14.399
an

00:10:14.399 --> 00:10:17.750
oxygen tank and ran up to me saying, "I've

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:19.910
been healed."I just

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:21.269
came back to tell you. I didn't know who

00:10:21.279 --> 00:10:23.750
he was because he wasn't

00:10:23.750 --> 00:10:23.760
ashy-looking.

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:25.990
His skin had pigment. He looked

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:28.949
great and I'll never forget it. I

00:10:28.959 --> 00:10:30.870
thought,

00:10:30.880 --> 00:10:34.389
"Wow, Jesus."As I went back into

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:35.910
some of the things the Lord has

00:10:35.910 --> 00:10:35.920
shown

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:38.389
us about healings and things that

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:41.030
are about to take place, I

00:10:41.030 --> 00:10:41.040
thought of

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.350
"can these bones

00:10:43.350 --> 00:10:43.360
live?"and

00:10:43.360 --> 00:10:45.350
the dead

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:50.310
in Christ

00:10:50.310 --> 00:10:50.320
rising

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:52.310
first. He

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:54.069
said, "Randy, you don't realize that

00:10:54.079 --> 00:10:57.030
all that which remains will

00:10:57.040 --> 00:10:58.710
be caught up. You don't know there's a

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:02.790
little bit of a gap

00:11:02.800 --> 00:11:04.870
there."There's

00:11:04.880 --> 00:11:06.710
a lot of people that talk about

00:11:06.710 --> 00:11:06.720
creation—that

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:10.150
whenever God made

00:11:10.160 --> 00:11:11.990
the earth, there's a gap between the

00:11:11.990 --> 00:11:12.000
verses,

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:15.350
between "let"and how the

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:18.069
dinosaurs ruled in that time frame. I

00:11:18.079 --> 00:11:20.230
think Rick Renner teaches it.

00:11:20.240 --> 00:11:22.389
I'll butcher it; I am not a

00:11:22.399 --> 00:11:24.150
theological

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:26.790
Greek person, but I know

00:11:26.800 --> 00:11:28.710
Rick Renner does that and he is very

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:31.030
gifted at it. He talks about

00:11:31.040 --> 00:11:34.310
creation and the gap. Dr. Carl

00:11:34.310 --> 00:11:34.320
Baugh,

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:35.910
I believe, is who it was. I remember

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:37.750
hearing him one day talking about

00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:39.030
the gap.

00:11:39.040 --> 00:11:41.110
But I was just trying to encourage you

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:44.069
all that God's moving,

00:11:44.079 --> 00:11:46.230
shaking, and doing things. I have

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:48.389
such an anticipation for these last days

00:11:48.399 --> 00:11:51.190
and what God's about to do. Billy

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:53.110
was saying he was believing God to have

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:56.150
a meeting here at the Mabee Center.

00:11:56.160 --> 00:11:58.630
Who would be interested? Let us know in the comments

00:11:58.640 --> 00:12:00.630
down below when you're on that live. Can

00:12:00.640 --> 00:12:03.269
you tell us if we had a meeting at

00:12:03.269 --> 00:12:03.279
ORU

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:05.829
and we rented out the

00:12:05.829 --> 00:12:05.839
Mabee

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:08.870
Center, would you come?

00:12:08.880 --> 00:12:10.870
I'm just curious before

00:12:10.880 --> 00:12:13.350
I take money and invest in it.

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:15.509
Would you come? Would you

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:17.110
like to have a healing

00:12:17.120 --> 00:12:18.949
meeting? I'll be there and

00:12:18.959 --> 00:12:20.710
I'll have to have

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:24.150
security, but

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:26.470
Billy Burke's going to do the services.

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:28.069
I'll be sitting

00:12:28.069 --> 00:12:28.079
in

00:12:28.079 --> 00:12:29.430
the congregation supporting him,

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:31.590
praying, and enjoying the

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:33.350
service. I won't be speaking,

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:36.230
but I believe in my friend

00:12:36.230 --> 00:12:36.240
and

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:39.509
the anointing on his life; I

00:12:39.519 --> 00:12:42.550
believe in the gift. It touches me.

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:46.150
After Megan went to

00:12:46.150 --> 00:12:46.160
Eufaula,

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:48.470
she no longer has plays in her

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:50.069
periods;

00:12:50.079 --> 00:12:53.030
Jesus is touching her. That's why

00:12:53.040 --> 00:12:55.190
I get so many little nuggets from

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:59.110
people. I always try to be a friend

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:01.990
to authentic people that really truly

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:05.350
love the Lord. I just

00:13:05.360 --> 00:13:07.190
wanted to throw that out there. I

00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:08.310
didn't know if there's anybody who would

00:13:08.320 --> 00:13:10.790
be interested in having a meeting,

